movie.title: From A to B
movie.writer: Ashraf Hamdi (contributing writer), Mohamed Hefzy (screenplay), Ronnie Khalil (contributing writer), Ali F. Mostafa (story)
movie.actors: Fahad Albutairi, Shadi Alfons, Fadi Rifaai, Khaled Abol Naga
movie.plot: Three estranged childhood friends (Omar, Ramy, Jay), travel on a road trip from Abu Dhabi to Beirut in memory of their lost friend. If what happens en route doesn't make them crazy, it might just bring them closer.
